{"tid":473830,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[Bio JJ 入] 究竟人喺日常情況會唔會用到腎上腺素","createTime":"2017-11-19T14:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T19:12:20.000Z","uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"da5521f30e626129339d3e9bb69ff0e11b05237c","tid":473830,"uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:27:30.000Z","msg":"我朋友係咁話佢同我打羽毛球嘅時侯會用到腎上腺素，究竟啱唔啱?<br />\n據我所知腎上腺素係危急關頭或者極度緊張嘅時候先會分泌，應該唔會比你話用就用，更加唔會響同朋友打友誼波嘅時候分泌，究竟我有冇錯，定係腎上腺素真係話用就用到既呢?<br />\n求bio jj解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e58774b0677411d24866ae8f8e1c27832a4c563","tid":473830,"uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"真心問㗎"},{"pid":"85f7430b2fb86623472703508109885c127ef57e","tid":473830,"uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:31:06.000Z","msg":"唔好負皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b422d81537efd4ec7dc9f70366a65153fcf5d9bd","tid":473830,"uid":85307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:33:05.000Z","msg":"其實日常生活一直都用緊<br />\n係緊急情況先會大量分泌"},{"pid":"2c31d5477172a6dc2ad4dd3d006960bb73b80f18","tid":473830,"uid":32380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:33:06.000Z","msg":"成日試做嘢做到好夜 就泌咗啲出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 時間慢咗個感覺好爽"},{"pid":"71c14d16edfbe2e606f982dfb79bb730339df3b8","tid":473830,"uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實日常生活一直都用緊<br />\n係緊急情況先會大量分泌</blockquote>佢意思係當佢打波嗰陣佢可以必啲腎上腺素出嚟喎"},{"pid":"bff38e903da380b733d00dfaaefc6c0e615ef6c2","tid":473830,"uid":132847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"應該唔係主動技嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9c176497e2ce949e9fe99abc0c3ad003e36d92","tid":473830,"uid":17623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:46:41.000Z","msg":"之前救人個陣<br />\n心跳得好快又大力<br />\n手震 耳鳴 <br />\n反應好左 <br />\n感覺好得人驚<br />\n平時應該好小會做到"},{"pid":"bbfec992f943f25b824907a195a5914b888ea136","tid":473830,"uid":20222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"等睇d 小學雞/手波撚話入左zone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bf01caaad10ba12ab1af87e1ff54a05ef63b90","tid":473830,"uid":97598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T16:12:15.000Z","msg":"正確概念應該係：<br />\n1. 人幾時都會分泌腎上腺素(又或者簡單啲諗：血液循環任何時候都會有腎上腺素)，只係分泌量會有變化(即係有時多啲/有時少啲)<br />\n<br />\n2. 處於壓力(例如比賽/競技)係會增加腎上腺素分泌，但唔係自己意志決定增加所以增加，而係壓力刺激神經系統，神經系統再傳遞一啲物質俾腎上腺，令腎上腺素分泌上升。"},{"pid":"bf685b3a3cdefce9e4c70c97c8f6d5b9e385aec2","tid":473830,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心問㗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmid term前一晚，deadline 前一晚，同埋 turnitin 30% 嘅時候 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a3c4cfa82e84a6a1fbcfcfbba4eeaa1e4d349c","tid":473830,"uid":104389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:08:15.000Z","msg":"正常打波唔會用到 除非佢就嚟暈低"},{"pid":"acb7b609778ea9e9a36b0ce2c410050e994fa39e","tid":473830,"uid":96077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:36:15.000Z","msg":"epinephrine can be used as a neurotransmitter, particularly in cotransmission to act on adrenergic receptors. it is not just secreted in the adrenal gland."},{"pid":"e3d4b7220fd5ffc83e5eb0135e57112484f4fe4a","tid":473830,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T19:12:20.000Z","msg":"咁打機突然去到緊急關頭個心跳得好快果幾秒係唔係腎上腺數上升？"}]}